# App Reality Report - SOP Manager V2

This report documents the actual implementation of the SOP Manager V2 codebase as of March 27, 2026.

---

## 1. ROUTES AND PAGES

List of existing routes, their authentication requirements, and functionality:

| URL Path | Auth Required | Roles | Loading.tsx | Error.tsx | Description |
|----------|---------------|-------|-------------|-----------|-------------|
| `/` | No | All | No | No | Root proxy that redirects to `/dashboard` or `/login`. |
| `/login` | No | All | No | No | User login page with Google OAuth support. |
| `/signup` | No | All | No | No | User registration page. |
| `/setup` | No | All | No | No | First-time administrator setup page. |
| `/onboarding` | Yes | All | No | No | 4-step wizard for new users to complete their profile and signature. |
| `/dashboard` | Yes | All | Yes | Yes | Main overview with KPI cards and activity feed. |
| `/library` | Yes | All | Yes | Yes | SOP Library with TanStack table and status filters. |
| `/library/[id]` | Yes | All* | Yes | No | SOP Viewer showing document and acknowledgement history. |
| `/approvals` | Yes | QA | Yes | Yes | Queue of SOP and Equipment requests pending QA review. |
| `/approvals/[id]` | Yes | QA | Yes | No | Detailed review page for a specific approval request. |
| `/change-control/[id]` | Yes | All | Yes | No | Change control page with diff viewer and signature grid. |
| `/equipment` | Yes | All | Yes | Yes | Registry of assets and PM tasks with status indicators. |
| `/equipment/[id]` | Yes | All | Yes | Yes | Equipment detail page with service history and QR code. |
| `/calendar` | Yes | All | Yes | Yes | Company calendar featuring manual events and auto-generated PM dates. |
| `/reports` | Yes | Manager/QA | Yes | Yes | Reporting hub with CSV export for audit and compliance data. |
| `/settings` | Yes | All | Yes | Yes | User profile management and admin tools (Departments/Users). |
| `/messages` | Yes | All | No | No | Real-time messaging system for direct and group conversations. |
| `/docs` | No | All | No | No | Documentation home page. |
| `/docs/[...slug]` | No | All | No | No | Dynamic documentation pages rendered from MDX. |

*\*Access to specific SOPs is governed by RLS (Department-based).*

