## 2. DATABASE TABLES

Total tables: 18 (excluding Supabase internal/auth tables).

### `departments`
- **RLS Enabled:** Yes (Select: All active users, Insert/Update/Delete: Admins)
- **Columns:**
  - [id](file:///e:/Projects/sop-manager-v2/components/app-sidebar.tsx#30-191) (uuid, primary key)
  - `name` (text, unique)
  - `colour` (text)
  - `is_qa` (boolean, default false)
  - `created_at` (timestamptz)
- **Triggers:** None
- **Indexes:** `departments_name_key` (unique)

### `profiles`
